{"tid":1397142,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"各位買裝備嘅巴打 請入！","createTime":"2019-08-02T10:39:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-02T14:27:42.000Z","uid":144964,"like":80,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"53426879980b13c9dbb7449109c088407e425f45","tid":1397142,"uid":144964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T10:39:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NEZHwXH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNEZHwXH.png&h=9f03d21f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n頭先同幾個前線手足去買眼罩，見到有個型號幾好<br />\nGG501，比較密封，冇咁易滲入氣體<br />\n但零零舍舍呢款冇寫價錢<br />\n咁我哋預貴極都只係幾十，因為其他3M眼罩都係十幾蚊至幾十蚊。<br />\n然後店員問我哋要幾多個，我哋就要咗接近十個<br />\n之後佢拎完俾我哋話$180一個<br />\n我哋仲有買一個單咀口罩，本身都係預一百幾蚊買到<br />\n點知店員開價開到300幾接近400蚊<br />\n最後埋單成千幾蚊<br />\n我哋幾個手足上網check返眼罩喺網到買只要80蚊左右<br />\n間舖食水好深<br />\n大家如非必要 唔好俾人昆<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7abff2a88bef05d1c4b3baa7e821e027f6e52e4c","tid":1397142,"uid":144964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T10:39:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"871edd159d974d0956cb239989cff744ed82d76a","tid":1397142,"uid":213101,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T10:40:07.000Z","msg":"推 黑店"},{"pid":"9f8dd1cf6a716f217bbe758719b0e0442050e038","tid":1397142,"uid":144964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T10:40:08.000Z","msg":"光復"},{"pid":"22a10c1c2dd2962556a17fe8d78caedc745586a2","tid":1397142,"uid":144964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T10:40:18.000Z","msg":"香港"},{"pid":"76f367093d8a9e3018ba5744369068eb494ef30d","tid":1397142,"uid":144964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T10:40:28.000Z","msg":"時代"},{"pid":"165de90f3260a0d82232519ded73948b776fc594","tid":1397142,"uid":203889,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7abff2a88bef05d1c4b3baa7e821e027f6e52e4c","tid":1397142,"uid":144964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyT